text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

The woman is a young woman who is trying to find her place in the world. The reason it never worked out with the men she dated was because they were all the same man. But that man, the shapeshifter, just could never seem to figure out why.  One day, she discovered his secret when he started talking about it in his sleep. She wasn't sure what to do with the information, but she knew she couldn't let him know she knew. So she decided to play along, and see where it went. 
Right away she remembered something. She remembered why it didn't work out with the other versions of this man. She remembered what she didn't like about him. The think that she never liked about the men were that they were all bad dressers. The woman really cared about fashion sense and after a while the bad fashion got on her nerves. She decided to confront him about it.
When he discovered the truth about why it never worked with the other versions of himself he thought the woman was very shallow. He was very upset that she would judge him on something so superficial. After this, the shapeshifter moved on and didn't ever pursue the woman again. And he lived happily from then on.
